NG0467:1: le'u ste lnga pa'o // // rtsa dang rlung la
NG0467:3: sems can dran zhing tsit+ta'i dkyil //
NG0467:4: chos gsum 'od kyi ngo bor shad //
NG0467:5: bskal pa bar ma la sangs rgyas 'od srungs kyis
NG0467:6: thog ma'i sangs rgyas 'od mi 'gyur ba'i zhal ma

NG0467:11: gsang ba thig le rten pa'i rtsa'o //

NG0467:13: bsdus pas ngo sprod gsum du 'dus //
NG0467:14: rlung la yang phyi nang gsang ba gsum //
NG0467:15: phyi rlung thams cad nang rlung snang ba yin //
NG0467:16: nang rlung ye shes rlung gi rtsal //
NG0467:17: gsang ba'i rlung chen ngos zin na //

NG0467:24: gnad du 'dzin pa rig pa'i ye shes yin //
NG0467:25: gnyis med lhangs kyis rtogs pa ye shes rlung du shes //
NG0467:26: gzung 'dzin gnyis su spyod pa ma rig rlung du shes //
NG0467:27: rtsa rlung thig le la ngo sprad pa'i mtshan ma
NG0467:28: lam ba'i rtsol sgrub la mi rten pa'i le'u ste
NG0467:29: drug pa'o // // ston pa gsum 'khor bar dus
NG0467:30: gcig la 'khyams pa ya mtshan che /
NG0467:31: 'byed pa med pa gti mug rang bzhin gyi ston pa /
NG0467:32: 'gag pa med pa'i zhe sdang ngo bo nyid kyi ston pa /
NG0467:33: rang snang chen po'i rtsal mi 'gag pa 'od chags thugs rje'i ston pa /
NG0467:34: rtsal 'gag pa med pa dug lnga thugs rje'i rol
NG0467:35: pa ma 'gags pa 'gro drug / rag bzhin chos
NG0467:38: sku gsum 'khor bar 'khyams kyang snying po la 'gyur ba med /
NG0467:40: gnas lugs la ngo sprad pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o
NG0467:41: // // bskal pa tha ma la sras gsum gyis
NG0467:42: 'thabs pas skad cig ma la 'khor ba thams cad
NG0467:43: dus gcig tu srog bcad nas me chen gyis bsregs
NG0467:44: / rlung chen gyis phyags pa de ya cha /
NG0467:45: ye shes chen po'i spyan gnyis 'dzin med par rang gsal /
NG0467:46: chos kyi spyan bar do med par rang gdangs /
NG0467:47: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyan cir snang cing 'dzin ye shes /
NG0467:48: ma bsgrubs ma btsal yin pa'i spyan gsal lo //

NG0467:50: ye shes kyi spyan chos skur ngo sprad /
NG0467:51: chos nyid kyi spyan longs skur ngo sprad /
NG0467:52: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyan sprul skur ngo sprad /
NG0467:53: ngo sprad pa man ngag gi rgyud kyi 'dug tshul ni /
NG0467:54: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum las ma 'das /
NG0467:55: spyan gsum rang la gnas pa ni ye shes kyi
NG0467:56: spyan ni rig pa'i ye shes lhangs kyis rtogs pa'o
NG0467:59: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyan ni thams cad rang gi 'dug tshul las ma 'das bar shes pa'o //
NG0467:60: spyan gsum khong du chud pas theg pa rim pa
NG0467:61: brgyad kyi rtsol sgrub kyi chos dang mu stegs rtag
NG0467:62: chad dang */ rdzogs chen kha 'byam bzhi la dgongs
NG0467:63: pa las kyi dbang mi btsan zer ba las shan
NG0467:64: chad dang */ phye ste / chos sku mkha' khyab
NG0467:65: dwangs pa spyan gsum 'dug tshul gcig tu bstan pas

NG0467:68: 'das pa gsum du ngo sprad pa ste /

NG0467:70: yul las 'das pa'i chos sku mkha' khyab dwangs pa /

NG0467:74: sleb nas 'gro sa ma rnyed pa de ya cha
NG0467:75: / thog ma'i ston pa 'od mi 'gyur bas gcung po gnyis la bos pa /
NG0467:76: kye kye grogs po bsam rdugs kyi lha khang du sleb pas 'gro sa med pa ya cha /
NG0467:77: chos sku mkha' khyab dwangs pas btsal ba ya cha /
NG0467:78: chos sku bsgrubs pasa'abras bu stor ba ya cha /
NG0467:79: rtsol sgrub mang po byas pas dri mas gtums pa de ya cha /
NG0467:81: ston pa 'od srungs kyi zhal nas /

NG0467:84: chos sku mkha' khyab dwangs par chas yin pas btsal du med pa ya cha /

NG0467:86: ye shes rang grol du shar nas ston pa gsum

NG0467:88: rgyas pa ni ya cha gsung ngo *//
NG0467:89: ston pa mar me mdzad kyi zhal nas /

NG0467:96: phung po bor bas dus kyi mtha' zad pa ya cha /

NG0467:104: phyi'i snang ba lha dang lha mo /

NG0467:113: par bstan pas tshig dbang rin po che'i dbang dus
NG0467:114: gcig la thob pa yin no //

NG0467:126: bsrung mtshams thams cad dus gcig bsrungs pa yin //
NG0467:127: lha rnams bskyed dang dkyil 'khor sgom pa dang *//

NG0467:131: mkhan gyi bu mo thams cad srog gcad nas gcig

NG0467:141: sangs rgya 'od srungs mjal nas bsgros pas khong gnyis
NG0467:142: grogs po byas pas ston pa'i sa bzung nas 'khor
NG0467:143: rigs lnga la chos ston pa ya cha /

NG0467:152: zhal gzigs nas ston pa gnyis la ma chags par
NG0467:153: spyad kyis song ba ya mtshan che /
